euclids algorithm, where num3 is the answer
drawing function import
drawing speed fastest

custom move function
custom colour function

length and width = fnum and snum
set canvas size to length and width

move to -(length / 2) and (width / 2)

set custom pen colour and size
forward length
turn left
forward width
turn left
forward length
turn left
forward width

NoBL Number of Boxes in x axis
NoBW = Number of Boxes in y axis
BS = num3

loop for NoBL

    loop for NoBW
        forward num3
        left
        forward num3
        left
        forward num3
        left
        forward num3
        left
        forward num3

    side_length = length divided by 2
    side_width = width divided by 2 - BS
    BS += num3
    custom move -side_length x, side_width y
